        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Nothing empowers me more than an ominous random task from the past me. We shall fulfill the past's wishes and embark on a random trip to one of the three summits of Mont Royal. I arbitrarily chose Belvédère-Kondiaronk for this one."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "After work, I took the bus to the cemetery at the top of Mont Royal. It took 10 minutes-ish of not slipping to reach the chalet. I am not that insane to be climbing in a single digit temperature with slippery ice."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "link",
              "title": null,
              "url": "https://photos.reinhardluvr69.com/photos/0547f294-9c56-4067-af15-5325e65865c9.jpg",
